OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPublic sector pay: Millions
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fof workers await deal      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdecision                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is due to unveil this   
OL,6, year's pay deal for 2.5 million public 
OL,7, sector workers.                        
OL,9,FThe awards cover one in four public    
OL,10,Fservants, including teachers, nurses,  
OL,11,Fdoctors, police officers, and members  
OL,12,Fof the armed forces.                   
OL,14,FUnions are pressing for pay to reflect 
OL,15,Fthe cost of living, as inflation rises 
OL,16,Fat the fastest rate for 40 years.      
OL,18,FBut ministers have signalled awards    
OL,19,Fwill not match price rises, warning    
OL,20,Fthis would push inflation even higher. 
